繼 2011
年二月十七日上午向巴林首都麥納瑪珍珠圓環的抗議群眾發動[突襲](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/02/17/bahrain-
breaking-news-police-attack-protesters-at-pearl-roundabout/
"https://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/02/17/bahrain-breaking-news-police-
attack-protesters-at-pearl-roundabout/")之後，有報導指出軍方坦克車正向首都前進。

